# Trivy CVE exceptions for orkyo-community
#
# Format:
#   CVE-YYYY-NNNNN  # Impact | Reason | Added: YYYY-MM-DD | Review: YYYY-MM-DD
#
# Policy: time-bound only. Review date must be within 14 days of added date.
# Remove entries once the upstream fix is available.

# ── Keycloak base image JDK (quay.io/keycloak/keycloak:26.6.2 / ubi9) ────────
# The Keycloak image ships without a package manager (microdnf absent in 26.x).
# OS packages cannot be upgraded from within the Dockerfile.
# Fix requires Keycloak to ship a new base image with updated ubi9 packages.
#
# Resolved in 26.6.2: CVE-2026-22016 (JDK 21.0.11), netty 4.1.132
# (CVE-2026-33870/33871/42579/42583/42584/42587), quarkus 3.33.1.1
# (CVE-2026-39852), bcprov 1.84 (CVE-2026-5598), pgjdbc 42.7.11 (CVE-2026-42198).

# java-21-openjdk-headless — Oracle CPU patches not yet in KC 26.6.2 ubi9 base
