# ── Keycloak embedded JARs (quay.io/keycloak/keycloak:26.6.2) ────────────────
# netty-transport-native-epoll: CVE fix requires 4.2.13; KC 26.6.2 ships 4.1.132.
CVE-2026-42577  # HIGH | netty-transport-native-epoll: DoS via RST on half-closed TCP — KC 26.6.2 ships netty 4.1.132; fix requires 4.2.13 | Added: 2026-05-21 | Review: 2026-06-04

