# Trivy reports fix as 12.6.5 but KC 26.6.2 ships mssql-jdbc 13.2.1 (newer); false positive.
CVE-2025-59250  # HIGH | mssql-jdbc: improper input validation — Trivy lists fix as 12.6.5 but KC ships 13.2.1 (newer); false positive | Added: 2026-05-21 | Review: 2026-06-04
